                        <li><strong>Secure Space:</strong> Ensure your home and yard are secure to prevent your dog from
                            escaping or getting into dangerous substances or plants.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <h3>Regular Exercise</h3>
                <div>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Daily Exercise:</strong> Dogs need regular physical activity to stay healthy and
                            happy. The amount varies by breed, size, and age.</li>
                        <li><strong>Playtime:</strong> Interactive play helps with bonding and keeps your dog mentally
                            stimulated.
                        </li>
                        <li><strong>Grooming</strong> Brush your cat regularly to reduce shedding and hairballs.
                            Long-haired breeds may require more frequent grooming.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
